header.title: Day-ahead prices
header.description: Changes in the Norwegian bidding areas can affect which geographical area the city references apply to (see the area change log pdf.) Please note – all prices shown are wholesale and exclude any fees, charges or taxes applied at a national level. All prices are in CET/CEST.
header.questionMarkInfo:
Day-ahead prices represent the result of Nord Pool's day-ahead implicit auction market. 

 

 

 

Peak = 09:00 to 20:00

Off peak 1 = 01:00 to 08:00

Off peak 2 = 21:00 to 24:00

Average = arithmetic average
